```
# create a directory for the app and cd to it
mkdir car-app && cd car-app
# run the jhipster wizard
yo jhipster
```

```
# runs entity creation wizard
yo jhipster:entity car
```

```

mkdir gateway-app && cd gateway-app

yo jhipster
```

```
# Runs entity creation wizard
yo jhipster:entity car
```
